dublin_core.dcvalue: The Liga Inan Mobile Moms Project is using mobile phones to connect expectant mothers with health care providers in Timor Leste to improve the likelihood of a healthy pregnancy and birth The goal of the Liga Inan project is to increase utilization of quality skilled care before during and after delivery
